        <h4><a class="taggedlink linklink" href="http://www.holovaty.com/blog/archive/2007/07/06/0128">Introducing templatemaker</a></h4>

        
            
        

        <p>Python library that analyses a corpus of web pages, works out where the dynamic values are in the template, then allows you to scrape out the juicy details.  I can think of oh, so many uses for this.</p>

